{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 [A tool for REAPER that splits stereo audio tracks into separate Mid and Side components. It automatically creates a new track folder with the original, Mid, and Side tracks, which are then routed to the master track. The script also includes options to preserve item colors, add a spectrum analyzer, or apply an EQ optimization for vocals. Instructions: Select one or more stereo audio tracks and run the script. The script will handle the rest.]\par}
}

